  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE GAME</h2><br>You are Landon — trapped in a twisted and terrifying dream, wondering a mysterious old house. Warm memories and terrible realities are intertwined and tragedy unfolds as you explore, find clues and solve puzzles in this long-forgotten nightmare.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/89c62400b7c3638b881e7c1d57232465.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/89c62400b7c3638b881e7c1d57232465.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/89c62400b7c3638b881e7c1d57232465.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><br>◼ A rich environment with atmospheric music and SFX for horror immersion<br>◼ Puzzles and hidden clues with moderate difficulty<br>◼ Terrifying animations and events; including some gore<br>◼ High-quality Chinese VO for an authentic Chinese horror experience<br>◼ Fully localised subtitles, UI and voiceovers<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/5286339efb7db7259a846e06bf0c8350.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/5286339efb7db7259a846e06bf0c8350.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/5286339efb7db7259a846e06bf0c8350.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY FEATURE</h2><br>Delve deep into your own inner world, confront the horrible truth about the tragic deaths of Lilith and her family. Your goal is to uncover a hidden conspiracy; the blood and sin that’s fuelled the success of an infamous cult known as Saint Cohen. A cruel sacrifice awaits you; the chains of flesh are foretelling your fate. With no way out, do you accept the fate or fight against it?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/e8fff2aece3e267841dc8596f4bb8d07.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/e8fff2aece3e267841dc8596f4bb8d07.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/e8fff2aece3e267841dc8596f4bb8d07.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR FEATURES</h2><br>◼ Supports HTC VIVE, Oculus Quest, Valve Index<br>◼ Improved VR movement with six degrees of freedom (6DOF)<br>◼ Full locomotion with snap-turning rotation<br>◼ Packed with interactive items; pick up, discard, knock or destroy<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/b762bccd2f60e70f9fa2d3098dab1d1f.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/b762bccd2f60e70f9fa2d3098dab1d1f.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/b762bccd2f60e70f9fa2d3098dab1d1f.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE GAME</h2><br>You are Landon — trapped in a twisted and terrifying dream, wondering a mysterious old house. Warm memories and terrible realities are intertwined and tragedy unfolds as you explore, find clues and solve puzzles in this long-forgotten nightmare.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/89c62400b7c3638b881e7c1d57232465.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/89c62400b7c3638b881e7c1d57232465.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/89c62400b7c3638b881e7c1d57232465.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><br>◼ A rich environment with atmospheric music and SFX for horror immersion<br>◼ Puzzles and hidden clues with moderate difficulty<br>◼ Terrifying animations and events; including some gore<br>◼ High-quality Chinese VO for an authentic Chinese horror experience<br>◼ Fully localised subtitles, UI and voiceovers<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/5286339efb7db7259a846e06bf0c8350.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/5286339efb7db7259a846e06bf0c8350.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/5286339efb7db7259a846e06bf0c8350.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY FEATURE</h2><br>Delve deep into your own inner world, confront the horrible truth about the tragic deaths of Lilith and her family. Your goal is to uncover a hidden conspiracy; the blood and sin that’s fuelled the success of an infamous cult known as Saint Cohen. A cruel sacrifice awaits you; the chains of flesh are foretelling your fate. With no way out, do you accept the fate or fight against it?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/e8fff2aece3e267841dc8596f4bb8d07.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/e8fff2aece3e267841dc8596f4bb8d07.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/e8fff2aece3e267841dc8596f4bb8d07.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR FEATURES</h2><br>◼ Supports HTC VIVE, Oculus Quest, Valve Index<br>◼ Improved VR movement with six degrees of freedom (6DOF)<br>◼ Full locomotion with snap-turning rotation<br>◼ Packed with interactive items; pick up, discard, knock or destroy<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/b762bccd2f60e70f9fa2d3098dab1d1f.poster.avif?t=1688115863\" width=618 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/b762bccd2f60e70f9fa2d3098dab1d1f.webm?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/b762bccd2f60e70f9fa2d3098dab1d1f.mp4?t=1688115863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
